# Changelog

## 17.4.4

* build on 17.4.6 base image
* add passenger related cronjobs
* add more munin plugins
* add a new nagios check
* reduce max-passenger-requests
* set TMPDIR to /var/tmp
* add rbpswatch
* fix IP_INTERNAL
* add ruby version to manifest

## 17.4.3

* rearange passenger options
* remove pkgsrc gems and install them directly
* move passenger config from vhost into global

## 17.4.2

* update to latest passenger 5.2.0
* add nrpe-local config

## 17.4.1

* build on latest base image 17.4.3
* add sphinx build script
* add redis and memcached

## 17.4.0

* First release